                "offerShortDescription": {
                    "text": "Eligible cardholders will be allowed 10 sessions of 1 hour each when they use their Visa Cards to purchase \"Golf training module\" at learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com.",
                    "richText": "<p>Eligible cardholders will be allowed 10 sessions of 1 hour each when they use their Visa Cards to purchase &quot;Golf training module&quot; at learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com.</p>"
                },
                "offerCopy": {
                    "text": "Eligible cardholders will be allowed 10 sessions of 1 hour each when they use their eligible cards issued in India to purchase “Golf training module” at learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com; with participating golf coaches and participating golf courses during the validity period, as per the below terms and conditions. These courses & coaches have tie ups with Golfgaga Greens Pvt Ltd who will manage this Learn Golf program. The company office is at G6, Blue Lotus, Road no3, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad 500034. - Access to golf courses & specifically the training/driving range. - Access to trained golf teachers /professionals at the selected golf course. - Personalized golf learning/coaching/practice sessions.",
                    "richText": "<p>Eligible cardholders will be allowed 10 sessions of 1 hour each when they use their eligible cards issued in India to purchase &ldquo;Golf training module&rdquo; at learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com; with participating golf coaches and participating golf courses during the validity period, as per the below terms and conditions. These courses &amp; coaches have tie ups with Golfgaga Greens Pvt Ltd who will manage this Learn Golf program. The company office is at G6, Blue Lotus, Road no3, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad 500034.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>- Access to golf courses &amp; specifically the training/driving range.<br />- Access to trained golf teachers /professionals at the selected golf course.<br />- Personalized golf learning/coaching/practice sessions.</p><script src=\"//merchantoffersresource.visa.com/morc/resources/js/ntpagetag.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">var NTPT_NOINITIALTAG=true;var NTPT_PGEXTRA='offer_id=116941&offer_revision_number=2';ntptEventTag();</script>"
                },
                "legalCountryExclusions": {
                    "text": "",
                    "richText": ""
