                "merchantTerms": {
                    "text": ".",
                    "richText": "<p>.</p>"
                },
                "visaTerms": {
                    "text": "- This Offer of learning golf through a “Golf training Module” is valid on Visa Cards (ONLY Visa Signature and Infinite Cards) issued by banks in India only. - This Offer is valid for the period starting from 1 January 2015 till 31 August 2017. - Golfgaga is providing the Offer hereunder for Visa Cardholders who have a valid Visa Signature or Visa Infinite Card. - The Offer will be provided by Golfgaga Greens Pvt Ltd .Offer details are at the url learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com - All purchases & payments have to be made on the said website by participating Cardholders (i.e. holder of a Visa Signature or Visa Infinite Card). - This Offer will be valid in 6 cities in India. The cities are Mumbai, Pune, Delhi /NCR, Kolkata, Chennai, Bengaluru & Hyderabad. If there is any update in the numbers of cities or names of cities, the same will be updated on the website. - The Offer will be made available at select golf courses in each city & will also identify golf coaches who will execute this program by providing teaching aids & training. - In case of any change in the golf courses that participate or in the names of coaches or trainers during the course of the Offer the same will be updated on the website. If there is a change in the coach an alternative coach will be provided. - Offers are valid for bookings made on the website for the Golf training module using a Visa Signature or a Visa Infinite Card only. Payments made through any other mode will not be eligible to avail the Offer. - This Offer can be purchased & is valid for anyone in the age group of 5 years to 65 years. - The Cardholder can avail the same for himself or for his family or friends or relatives. There is no limit in the number of Golf training packages /modules that a Cardholder can avail off during the validity period. - Once a “Golf training module” has been purchased the same must be availed off within 90 days of the date of purchase. The golf-training module consists of 10 sessions of 1 hour each. This will need to be scheduled with the coach & golf course. The Golfgaga concierge desk in consultation with the concerned club, coach & the participant, will do this. - Once purchased there will be no cancellation of a Golf training module under any circumstances. There will be no refunds for partly used or unused services. - Golfgaga shall not guarantee or be held responsible or liable for any delays in product or service execution being offered by the Golf course or Coach which are due to acts of god (weather delays / delays because of strikes etc) and which are not within the control of Golfgaga. - All disputes related to the offer shall be the subject matter of the jurisdiction of the Hyderabad High Court. The prevailing statutory laws of India shall be applicable to the Offer. - This offer cannot be combined with any other offer currently applicable on Golfgaga for the same or similar products. - There is no limit to the number of times this Offer can be utilized by a Cardholder.",
                    "richText": "<p>- This Offer of learning golf through a &ldquo;Golf training Module&rdquo; is valid on Visa Cards (ONLY Visa Signature and Infinite Cards) issued by banks in India only.<br />- This Offer is valid for the period starting from 1 January 2015 till 31 August 2017. <br />- Golfgaga is providing the Offer hereunder for Visa Cardholders who have a valid Visa Signature or Visa Infinite Card.<br />- The Offer will be provided by Golfgaga Greens Pvt Ltd .Offer details are at the url learngolfinindia.golfgaga.com<br />- All purchases &amp; payments have to be made on the said website by participating Cardholders (i.e. holder of a Visa Signature or Visa Infinite Card).<br />- This Offer will be valid in 6 cities in India. The cities are Mumbai, Pune, Delhi /NCR, Kolkata, Chennai, Bengaluru &amp; Hyderabad. If there is any update in the numbers of cities or names of cities, the same will be updated on the website.<br />- The Offer will be made available at select golf courses in each city &amp; will also identify golf coaches who will execute this program by providing teaching aids &amp; training. <br />- In case of any change in the golf courses that participate or in the names of coaches or trainers during the course of the Offer the same will be updated on the website. If there is a change in the coach an alternative coach will be provided.<br />- Offers are valid for bookings made on the website for the Golf training module using a Visa Signature or a Visa Infinite Card only. Payments made through any other mode will not be eligible to avail the Offer. <br />- This Offer can be purchased &amp; is valid for anyone in the age group of 5 years to 65 years.<br />- The Cardholder can avail the same for himself or for his family or friends or relatives. There is no limit in the number of Golf training packages /modules that a Cardholder can avail off during the validity period.<br />- Once a &ldquo;Golf training module&rdquo; has been purchased the same must be availed off within 90 days of the date of purchase. The golf-training module consists of 10 sessions of 1 hour each. This will need to be scheduled with the coach &amp; golf course. The Golfgaga concierge desk in consultation with the concerned club, coach &amp; the participant, will do this.<br />- Once purchased there will be no cancellation of a Golf training module under any circumstances. There will be no refunds for partly used or unused services.<br />- Golfgaga shall not guarantee or be held responsible or liable for any delays in product or service execution being offered by the Golf course or Coach which are due to acts of god (weather delays / delays because of strikes etc) and which are not within the control of Golfgaga.<br />- All disputes related to the offer shall be the subject matter of the jurisdiction of the Hyderabad High Court. The prevailing statutory laws of India shall be applicable to the Offer. <br />- This offer cannot be combined with any other offer currently applicable on Golfgaga for the same or similar products.<br />- There is no limit to the number of times this Offer can be utilized by a Cardholder.</p>"
