                "offerTitle": "Get up to 50% off on movie tickets only on Bookmyshow mobile app",
                "featuredOfferIndicator": false,
                "validityFromDate": "2015-02-02 00:00:00.0",
                "validityToDate": "2015-06-30 00:00:00.0",
                "promotionFromDate": "2015-02-02 00:00:00.0",
                "promotionToDate": "2015-06-30 00:00:00.0",
                "offerShortDescription": {
                    "text": "Get up to 50% off on movie tickets only on Bookmyshow mobile app",
                    "richText": "<p>Get up to 50% off on movie tickets only on Bookmyshow mobile app</p>"
                },
                "offerCopy": {
                    "text": "Get up to 50% off on movie tickets only on Bookmyshow mobile app. To avail, save & pay using your Visa Debit card. How to Avail the Offer on Mobile App: 1. Download the BookMyShow Mobile app. 2. New user has to ensure that the card is registered with QuikPay if not; the customer has to register his visa Debit card before making a transaction. 3. Process to Register on QuikPay - Go To “ YOU” tab on Bookmyshow mobile app - Select “QuikPay” from the list - Add your Visa Debit Card details as requested. - Your details will be stored safely and will be strictly confidential. - Card saved can be used for further transactions and to avail the “Visa Debit Card” offer. 4. An existing QuikPay user has to ensure that an eligible Visa Debit Card is saved on Quikpay and is subsequently used for transaction to avail the offer. 5. Follow the regular ticketing flow on the mobile app by selecting the movie, show and seat of your choice. 6. On Review screen select Visa Debit card on QuikPay and enter CVV. 7. You will see the list of offers. Select \"Visa Mobile App Offer\". 8. The discount will be applied to the transaction and you will be moved to the payment page to complete the transaction. 9. Congratulations! You would have successfully availed your offer. Important Note: 1. Offer valid on Visa Debit Card only. 2. Offer is available only if Visa Debit card is saved on QuikPay and tickets are booked through Bookmyshow mobile app. 3. Offer is valid on 3 movie transactions during the offer period - First Transaction : 10% off ,maximum discount up to INR 50/- - Second Transaction : 25% off, maximum discount up to INR 125/- - Third Transaction: 50% off, maximum discount up to INR 250/- 4. Offer is Valid for 35,000 customers who complete their 1st transaction under the offer based on monthly quotas. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer period irrespective of monthly quotas. 5. A customer’s quota will get exhausted after all 3 transactions or end of offer period whichever is earlier 6. Offer Period: 2-Feb 2015 to 30-June 2015 7. The customer will have to pay internet handling fee as levied on each ticket.",
                    "richText": "<p>Get up to 50% off on movie tickets only on Bookmyshow mobile app.<br />To avail, save &amp; pay using your Visa Debit card.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How to Avail the Offer on Mobile App:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Download the BookMyShow Mobile app.<br />2. New user has to ensure that the card is registered with QuikPay if not; the customer has to register his visa<br />Debit card before making a transaction.<br />3. Process to Register on QuikPay<br />- Go To &ldquo; YOU&rdquo; tab on Bookmyshow mobile app<br />- Select &ldquo;QuikPay&rdquo; from the list<br />- Add your Visa Debit Card details as requested.<br />- Your details will be stored safely and will be strictly confidential.<br />- Card saved can be used for further transactions and to avail the &ldquo;Visa Debit Card&rdquo; offer.<br />4. An existing QuikPay user has to ensure that an eligible Visa Debit Card is saved on Quikpay and is<br />subsequently used for transaction to avail the offer.<br />5. Follow the regular ticketing flow on the mobile app by selecting the movie, show and seat of your choice.<br />6. On Review screen select Visa Debit card on QuikPay and enter CVV.<br />7. You will see the list of offers. Select &quot;Visa Mobile App Offer&quot;.<br />8. The discount will be applied to the transaction and you will be moved to the payment page to complete the<br />transaction.<br />9. Congratulations! You would have successfully availed your offer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Important Note:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Offer valid on Visa Debit Card only.<br />2. Offer is available only if Visa Debit card is saved on QuikPay and tickets are booked through Bookmyshow<br />mobile app.<br />3. Offer is valid on 3 movie transactions during the offer period<br />- First Transaction : 10% off ,maximum discount up to INR 50/-<br />- Second Transaction : 25% off, maximum discount up to INR 125/-<br />- Third Transaction: 50% off, maximum discount up to INR 250/-<br />4. Offer is Valid for 35,000 customers who complete their 1st transaction under the offer based on monthly<br />quotas. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer<br />period irrespective of monthly quotas.<br />5. A customer&rsquo;s quota will get exhausted after all 3 transactions or end of offer period whichever is earlier<br />6. Offer Period: 2-Feb 2015 to 30-June 2015<br />7. The customer will have to pay internet handling fee as levied on each ticket.</p><script src=\"//merchantoffersresource.visa.com/morc/resources/js/ntpagetag.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">var NTPT_NOINITIALTAG=true;var NTPT_PGEXTRA='offer_id=114898&offer_revision_number=1';ntptEventTag();</script>"
                },
                "legalCountryExclusions": {
                    "text": "",
                    "richText": ""
                },
                "merchantTerms": {
                    "text": ".",
                    "richText": "<p>.</p>"
                },
                "visaTerms": {
                    "text": "- Customer will get a 10% off max discount up to INR 50/- on the first transaction, 25% off max discount of INR 125/- on the second transaction and 50% off with max discount of INR 250/- off on his third transaction done through his eligible Visa Debit card during the offer period. - Offer will only be available on the mobile app. - Offer is Valid for 35,000 customers who complete their 1st transaction under the offer based on monthly quotas. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer period irrespective of monthly quotas. - New user has to ensure that the card is registered with QuikPay if not the customer has to register his card before making a transaction. (Process of registering : In How To Avail offer section). - An existing QuikPay user has to ensure that an eligible Visa Debit Card is saved on Quikpay and is subsequently used for transaction to avail the offer. - The system will automatically check the customer’s transaction history and accordingly pass on the necessary discount provided all the terms and conditions and the eligibility criteria are fulfilled. - The offer is available on a first come first serve basis. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer period irrespective of monthly quotas. - In case you have applied for the discount but the transaction doesn't go through for some reason, kindly wait for 20 minutes before trying to avail the discount again. - The current purchase process at Bookmyshow mobile app will remain unchanged till the stage the offer is availed. After this stage, we will validate the card, reduce the discount amount and inform the eligible cardholder on the remaining amount to be paid using the same card. - Offer is applicable on all partner cinemas in India for which tickets can be booked on BookMyShow mobile app. - The offer cannot be combined with any offer/discounts/promotions at the theaters available on BookMyShow mobile app. - Tickets once bought online, shall be considered sold and cannot be cancelled, refunded or exchanged. - Once the booking is committed, the confirmation mail/SMS received from BookMyShow needs to be exchanged with the ticket available at the theater. - Bigtree & Visa reserves the right to disqualify any Card Holder/s from the benefits of the Program. If case of any fraudulent activity, prosecution will be carried according to the purpose of availing the benefits under the Program. - Bigtree & Visa reserves the right to modify/ change all or any of the terms applicable to the Program without assigning any reasons or without any prior intimation whatsoever. - Bigtree & Visa also reserves the right to discontinue the Program without assigning any reasons or without any prior intimation whatsoever. - Individual Cinema rules applicable. - In addition to the above, this offer on the website is also subject to BookMyShow's general Terms of Use. Kindly refer to BookMyShow's Terms & Conditions on the homepage. - The Cardholder shall be required to give personal information and card details online for the tickets purchased on www.bookmyshow.com. - Incase of any disputes, Bigtree's decision will be final. - Offer not valid on SME/Business Debit Cards.",
                    "richText": "<p>- Customer will get a 10% off max discount up to INR 50/- on the first transaction, 25% off max discount of INR 125/- on the second transaction and 50% off with max discount of INR 250/- off on his third transaction done through his eligible Visa Debit card during the offer period. <br />- Offer will only be available on the mobile app. <br />- Offer is Valid for 35,000 customers who complete their 1st transaction under the offer based on monthly quotas. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer period irrespective of monthly quotas. <br />- New user has to ensure that the card is registered with QuikPay if not the customer has to register his card before making a transaction. (Process of registering : In How To Avail offer section).<br />- An existing QuikPay user has to ensure that an eligible Visa Debit Card is saved on Quikpay and is subsequently used for transaction to avail the offer.<br />- The system will automatically check the customer&rsquo;s transaction history and accordingly pass on the necessary discount provided all the terms and conditions and the eligibility criteria are fulfilled.<br />- The offer is available on a first come first serve basis. Post that a customer can choose to do his 2nd and 3rd transaction at any time during the offer period irrespective of monthly quotas.<br />- In case you have applied for the discount but the transaction doesn't go through for some reason, kindly wait for 20 minutes before trying to avail the discount again.<br />- The current purchase process at Bookmyshow mobile app will remain unchanged till the stage the offer is availed. After this stage, we will validate the card, reduce the discount amount and inform the eligible cardholder on the remaining amount to be paid using the same card.<br />- Offer is applicable on all partner cinemas in India for which tickets can be booked on BookMyShow mobile app.<br />- The offer cannot be combined with any offer/discounts/promotions at the theaters available on BookMyShow mobile app.<br />- Tickets once bought online, shall be considered sold and cannot be cancelled, refunded or exchanged.<br />- Once the booking is committed, the confirmation mail/SMS received from BookMyShow needs to be exchanged with the ticket available at the theater.<br />- Bigtree &amp; Visa reserves the right to disqualify any Card Holder/s from the benefits of the Program. If case of any fraudulent activity, prosecution will be carried according to the purpose of availing the benefits under the Program.<br />- Bigtree &amp; Visa reserves the right to modify/ change all or any of the terms applicable to the Program without assigning any reasons or without any prior intimation whatsoever.<br />- Bigtree &amp; Visa also reserves the right to discontinue the Program without assigning any reasons or without any prior intimation whatsoever.<br />- Individual Cinema rules applicable.<br />- In addition to the above, this offer on the website is also subject to BookMyShow's general Terms of Use. Kindly refer to BookMyShow's Terms &amp; Conditions on the homepage.<br />- The Cardholder shall be required to give personal information and card details online for the tickets purchased on www.bookmyshow.com.<br />- Incase of any disputes, Bigtree's decision will be final.<br />- Offer not valid on SME/Business Debit Cards.</p>"
