                "offerCopy": {
                    "text": "Enjoy 15% off best available room rates, late checkout (upon availability), and up to 30% off at participating dining outlets during your stay, when you stay 2 or more nights at Sheraton or Westin branded Starwood Properties within the Asia Pacific region. Validity: - Bookings must be made between now and 31 August 2015 and stays and dining to be completed by 30 September 2015. - Cardholder has to book a minimum 2-night stay at any of the Sheraton or Westin branded Starwood Properties. - Cardholder must make full payment in advance for the eligible stay with a valid and eligible Visa Prepaid, Visa Classic, Visa Gold, Visa Platinum, Visa Rewards, Visa Signature, Visa Infinite or Visa Commercial card. Booking channels: Cardholder - Please book online directly at www.starwoodhotels.com/visa.",
